WEBVTT

00:07.474 --> 00:09.305
<i>Joseph Conrad once wrote.:</i>

00:13.079 --> 00:14.910
<i>''Who knows what true happiness is?</i>

00:18.084 --> 00:19.779
<i>''Not the conventional word...</i>

00:23.256 --> 00:25.121
<i>''but the naked terror.</i>

00:28.461 --> 00:31.396
<i>''To the lonely themselves,</i>
<i>it wears a mask.</i>

00:36.803 --> 00:41.797
<i>''The most miserable outcast</i>
<i>hugs some memory....</i>

00:47.380 --> 00:49.109
<i>''Or some illusion. ''</i>

